3) Each layer via density >= 1.66/um2,Top via density >=1.29/um2.
4) The vias in stacked via array interact with the same interlayer metal.
5) The 3-level continuous stacked via array means the stacked via array are 3 continuous via layers and corresponding 2 continuous stacked interlayer metals all have no metal cross (DRC waive width <= 2um metal line and check all interlayer metals projected space > 0um).
